parameters.name: 11恋愛パート・あこがれの人

parameters: Polka: "Yui-chan, are you really okay with this?"
Yui: "Yes. It's something Ginga and I decided on."

Polka: "If the two of you use the ultimate magic, the life taken might
be halved."

Polka: "But in the worst case, it could mean the end of both your
lives..."

Yui: "I can't explain it well, but I have a feeling that won't
happen."

Yui: "Besides, Ginga's hunches tend to be right. I'm willing to bet on
that."
Polka: "Please show me the Holy Brooch."

Yui: "It got damaged in the fight against Dargnoa... it's in this
state..."
Polka: "This is terrible. The gem part is shattered."

Polka: "In this condition, you can't even transform into Pony Ceres,
let alone use the ultimate magic."
Polka: "You were planning to go into battle like this?"
Polka: "I was planning to replace the gem part anyway."
Polka: "The head part of the brooch is made of a gem, right?"

Polka: "This gem is a special stone called a Light Stone. It's a
miraculous stone created by the goddess to put an end to the ancient
conflict between light and darkness."

Polka: "And it's said that there are three Light Stones in the
world--"
Polka: "One is missing, and one is the one you broke."
Polka: "And the last one is right here."
Polka: "If we set this new one in place..."
Polka: "Look, it's as good as new!"
Yui: "But you had one too, Polka..."
Polka: "Hm? Yes, but what about it?"

Yui: "You were always carrying that gamepad so carefully, I wondered
why. I never imagined it had a Light Stone inside..."

Polka: "I hid it just in case, for when Yui-chan broke her Holy
Brooch, for an emergency."
Polka: "Hehe, no one would think it's inside this, right?"

Polka: "Besides, if you think there's a spare, it doesn't feel as
special. The sense of superiority from being able to transform into
Pony Ceres is quite an important element!"

Polka: "I'm the only one who's the hero, Pony Ceres! That kind of
superiority feeling, you had it too, right~"

Yui: "I'm fighting Zaidar-G with my life on the line! I'm not
concerned about feeling special or superior every single time--!!"
Polka: "Fufufu, with that spirit, you might even defeat Darg-Noa!"

Polka: "It's good to see you back to your usual energetic self.
Welcome back, Yui-chan."

Polka: "Now, let's put the jokes aside... look, you can now use the
ultimate magic."
Polka: "My Light Stone is the one that can use the ultimate magic."

Polka: "It's a particularly special stone among the three Light
Stones. Take good care of it~"
Polka: "There's something I want you to keep in mind."

Polka: "I can feel Darg-Noa's immense power. It's probably a sign of
his complete revival..."

Polka: "Whether ultimate magic will work on a fully revived Darg-Noa
is something even I don't know."
Yui: "What? Then no one can defeat Darg-Noa?"

Polka: "If by any chance the ultimate magic doesn't work, we'd be in a
dire situation."

Polka: "You understand? We need to use the ultimate magic when Darg-
Noa is weakened as much as possible."

Polka: "You'll only get one chance, so use it when you think it's the
right moment."

Polka: "It's going to be a battle like nothing we've seen before.
It'll be intense enough to involve everyone around."

Polka: "So until that chance comes, I want Ginga to stay hidden in the
shadows."
Yui: "Understood. I'll corner Darg-Noa by myself first."
Polka: "That's the spirit! Do your best, Yui-chan!"
Polka: "Well, I'll go back underground. The rest is up to you two..."

Polka: "It might be the last time, so indulge in as much lovey-dovey
as you want! Fufufu"
